                  <summary>This manuscript is a collection of various mantras.  Front cover broken and with wormholes  Left upper margin 4 times : 
line 1 śrīgurubhyo namaḥ  
line 2 śrīguru(bhyo) namaḥ  
line 3. śrīguru(gap due to wormhole) namaḥ  
line 4. śrīgurubhyo namaḥ.
 Some writing is scribbled before the final cover.   </summary>
                  
